graph TB
    subgraph DSPO["Data Science Pipelines Operator"]
        Controller["DSPAReconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)<br/>MaxConcurrentReconciles: 10"]
        Templating["Manifestival Templating<br/>(config/internal/ Go templates)"]
        HealthCheck["Health Check System<br/>(DB + S3 probes, 15s timeout)"]
        ManagedPipelines["Managed Pipelines Fetcher<br/>(OCI image, 10min cache)"]
        Controller -->|renders templates| Templating
        Controller -->|probes backends| HealthCheck
        Controller -->|fetches manifests| ManagedPipelines
    end

    User[User / Dashboard] -->|creates| DSPACR["DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR"]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller

    subgraph DSPStack["Deployed DSP Stack (per DSPA namespace)"]
        direction TB
        subgraph APILayer["API Layer"]
            APIServer["ds-pipeline-api-server<br/>8888/TCP REST, 8887/TCP gRPC"]
            KubeRBACProxy["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP (sidecar)"]
            KubeRBACProxy -->|SAR auth → proxy| APIServer
        end

        subgraph Orchestration["Orchestration"]
            ArgoController["ds-pipeline-workflow-controller<br/>(Argo Workflows 3.6.12)"]
            PersistenceAgent["ds-pipeline-persistenceagent<br/>(syncs Workflow → DB)"]
            ScheduledWorkflow["ds-pipeline-scheduledworkflow<br/>(cron → Argo Workflow)"]
        end

        subgraph MLMD["ML Metadata"]
            MLMDgRPC["ds-pipeline-metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC"]
            MLMDEnvoy["ds-pipeline-metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP + kube-rbac-proxy 8443"]
            MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
        end

        subgraph Storage["Storage (optional managed)"]
            MariaDB["MariaDB 10.5<br/>3306/TCP"]
            MinIO["MinIO<br/>9000/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph Webhook["Webhook (conditional)"]
            DSPWebhook["ds-pipelines-webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS"]
        end
    end

    Controller -->|deploys & manages| DSPStack

    APIServer -->|reads/writes| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|stores/retrieves artifacts| MinIO
    MLMDgRPC -->|reads/writes lineage| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| APIServer
    ArgoController -->|creates/manages| PipelinePods["Pipeline Pods<br/>(launcher/driver)"]
    PipelinePods -->|logs lineage| MLMDgRPC
    PipelinePods -->|stores artifacts| MinIO

    subgraph ExternalRoutes["OpenShift Routes (TLS Reencrypt)"]
        APIRoute["ds-pipeline Route<br/>443 → 8443"]
        MLMDRoute["ds-pipeline-md Route<br/>443 → 8443"]
    end

    APIRoute -->|external access| KubeRBACProxy
    MLMDRoute -->|external access| MLMDEnvoy

    InitManagedPipelines["init-managed-pipelines<br/>(init container)"] -->|extracts pipelines| APIServer

    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"] -.->|CRUD operations| Controller
    ArgoController -.->|manages Workflows| K8sAPI

